      "content": "wait why are you being so intense lol i didn't say i was in a crisis, i just asked about a supplement. i'm not looking for a helpline, i just want to know if it's actually dangerous. like, isn't it mostly just mild stuff when it's herbal? i'm just looking for some info so i can make a decision.",
